    <title>Filling the Gap: The Consequences of Collaborator Loss in Corporate R&amp;amp;D</title>
    <updated>2026-02-21T14:04:39+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Felix Poege, Fabian Gaessler, Karin Hoisl, Dietmar Harhoff, Matthias Dorner</name>
