    <title>How Do Different Remote Work Arrangements Impact Employee Job Satisfaction and Retention?</title>
    <updated>2026-02-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Christos A. Makridis, Jason Schloetzer</name>
