    <title>Social media discussion of sell-side analyst research: evidence from Twitter</title>
    <updated>2026-02-09T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Andrew C. Call, Mehmet C. Kara, Matt Peterson, Eric Weisbrod</name>
